descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This dataset displays the location of environmental corridors that limit development. Generally speaking an environmental corridor is protected resource and follows wetland buffers, floodplain boundaries and natural resource protection areas.]
descript.abstract: This data layer represents environmental corridors in Dane County, WI in 2018. [Environmental corridors for the Capital Area Regional Planning Commission areas.]

dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This dataset displays the location of environmental corridors that limit development. Generally speaking an environmental corridor is protected resource and follows wetland buffers, floodplain boundaries and natural resource protection areas.]
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents environmental corridors in Dane County, WI in 2018. [Environmental corridors for the Capital Area Regional Planning Commission areas.]
